pylapp.smoothclicker.android.notifiers

Class StatusBarNotifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • pylapp.smoothclicker.android.notifiers.StatusBarNotifier

  • public class StatusBarNotifier
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class which manages notifications in the status bar. It is based on a wrapper design pattern.
    Since:
    16/03/2016
    Version:
    2.2.0
    Author:
    pylapp

    • Method Detail

      • makeNotification

        public void makeNotification(StatusBarNotifier.NotificationTypes type,
                             long... params)
        Makes a unmovable notification with a dedicated LED color. This notification is an "on going" one, and should be displayed will the app is clicking.
        Parameters:
        type - - The notification type
        params - -
        • For CLICK_MADE :params[0] for the X coordinate, params[1] for the Y coordinate
        • For COUNT_DOWN :params[0] for the leaving time to display
        • Nothing otherwise

      • removeAllNotifications
